employing veterans cognizant technology solutions is a coalition member of the veteran jobs mission this coalition participates in a collective initiative to hire  transitioning service members and military veterans by the year  as a coalition member cognizant is proud to commit to the effort of providing career opportunities for united states veterans for more information on the initiative and for veteran career resources visit veteran jobs mission corporate culture create and develop an understanding and appreciation of military culture within cognizant leadership train leaders and managers on how to effectively interview train and manage veterans recruitment increase our veteran headcount through veteranspecific sourcing channels and methods onboarding assimilate veterans to cognizant culture and ensure smooth integration into new role career growthsupport guide veterans on a career path within cognizant and extend additional support to ensure retention recognition through our efforts across camo to cognizants  strategic areas our goal is to achieve veteran and military employee career success enhancing our corporate brand and becoming known in veteran circles as a world class veteran career source x each of our locations has a digital wall of honor displaying our highly valued veterans of cognizant cognizant proudly partners with donors choose and provides funding to teachers of military children we are honored members of the  jobs mission coalition cognizant has been named a  military friendly employer x userra training promotion path for veterans cultural norms training for hiring managers and newly hired veterans x veteran job fairs we are attending coming soon x we have a teamup service that places new veterans with current cognizant veterans to help adjust during the onboarding process all newly hired veterans are given the opportunity to join our company wide veteran affinity group x veteran mentor program affinity group tailored benefits for veterans depl