cing liberty global the most recent short interest data has been released for the  settlement date and we here at dividend channel like to sift through this fresh data and order the underlying components of the nasdaq  by days to cover there are a number of ways to look at short data for example the total number of shares short but one metric that we find particularly useful is the days to cover metric because it considers both the total shares short and the average daily volume of shares typically traded the number of shares short is then compared to the average daily volume in order to calculate the total number of trading days it would take to close out all of the open short positions if every share traded represented a short position being closed apr    pm edt cognizant schedules first quarter  earnings release and conference call apr    am edt abn amro clearing selects cognizant as strategic partner to cloudenable global it infrastructure apr    am edt hb application window closes after just days for fourth year in a row outsourcers such as infosys and cognizant are big hirers of hb visa holders but alphabet apple and other major tech names have also used special visas to hire foreign workers apr    am edt buy accentures stock on dips investors are advised to wait for a  pullback before venturing into accenture apr    pm edt cognizant names betsy atkins and john dineen to board of directors mar    am edt next load more quant rating on  pm edt  b buy get the ctsh report here from our partners accenture acn closes consultancy firm labanswer buyout zacks visa cognizant added to best ideas list fis removed at wedbush the fly wedgewood partners q client letter  the fab five seekingalpha it services companies can benefit from ai opportunity says keybanc the fly genpact cora to enhance enterprises digital capabilities zacks heres why you should hold on to accenture acn stock now zacks apple and stratasys taking stock with tech seekingalpha accenture acn q earnings and