structure services  fathom consulting canada april  telecom  automotive it services  ygyan consulting india february  sap consulting  infopulse netherlands december  it services  aces international us april  siebel crm consulting  american express travelrelated services account from silverline technologies us sep  financial services  unitedhealthcare ireland limited ireland june  healthcare services a subsidiary of the unitedhealth group  servicesedit cognizant provides information technology information security consulting ito and bpo services these include business  technology consulting systems integration application development  maintenance it infrastructure services analytics business intelligence data warehousing customer relationship management supply chain management engineering  manufacturing solutions enterprise resource planning research and development outsourcing and testing solutions cognizant digital works — created to help clients rapidly build pilot and scale enterpriselevel digital initiatives — is central to cognizants efforts to help clients drive business change across their operations and inform their gotomarket activities business modeledit cognizants original corporate headquarters in chennai now an offshore delivery center like many other it services firms cognizant follows a global delivery model based on offshore software rd and offshore outsourcing the company has a number of offshore development centers outside the united states and nearshore centers in the us europe and south america in its early years cognizant gained business from a number of american and european companies with the help of the dun  bradstreet brand the companys senior executives envisaged the firm as a provider of highend customer services onpar with the six contemporary major system integrators accenture bearingpoint capgemini ey deloitte and ibm but at lower prices outsourcing controversy and hiring in the usedit cognizant is number one in top  companies receiving hb visas to bring immigrant workers to the united states the company has been steadily increasing its us work force in january  the company announced plans to expand its us delivery centers including a new person facility in phoenix arizona in february  cognizant said it had  fulltime recruiters actively hiring in the us in  an investigation by the us department of labor dol found cognizant in violation of the hb provisions of the immigration and nationality administrative act dol found that  of its workers hired under the hb program were underpaid according to cognizant this was due to unintentional administrative errors the dol investigation revealed that cognizant had achieved  compliance in its management of hb visarelated issues the company paid us in back wages to the  employees no fines or visa restrictions were imposed since dol did not discover any willful violations joseph petrecca the director of the wage and hour divisions northern new jersey district office praised the company for taking immediate steps to correct the violations this level of cooperation sets a standard for others in the industry in  the company was the subject of a lawsuit by workers for walt disney world who said workers from india were brought into the united states on hb visas in order to replace them however in october  federal judge gregory a presnel of the united states district court in orlando has dismissed the lawsuits stating none of the allegedly false statements put at issue in the complaint are adequate operationsedit regionsedit in addition to its global headquarters and delivery center in teaneck new jersey and the us headquarters in college station texas cognizant has  other us delivery centers bentonville arkansas bridgewater new jersey des moines iowa holliston massachusetts minot north dakota phoenix arizona southfield michigan williston vermont st louis missouri union new jersey sacramento california charlotte north carolina oklahoma city oklahoma washington pennsylvania malvern pennsylvania naperville illinois carmel indiana linthicum maryland and tampa florida the company has more than  employees globally of which over  are in india across  locations with a plurality in chennai the other centers of the company are in bangalore coimbatore gurgaon noida hyderabad kochi kolkata mangalore mumbai and pune the company has local regional and global delivery centers in the uk hungary the netherlands spain china philippines canada brazil argentina mexico etc business unitsedit cognizant is organized into several verticals and horizontal units the vertical units focus on specific industries such as banking  financial services healthcare manufacturing and retail the horizontals focus on specific technologies or process areas such as analytics mobile computing bpo and testing both horizontal and vertical units have business consultants who together form the organizationwide cognizant business consulting cbc team cognizant is among the largest recruiters of mbas in the industry they are involved in business development and business analysis for it services projects according to the  financial statements the major portion of cognizants revenues is derived from clients in the financial services  and healthcare  industries other substantial revenue sources include clients from manufacturing retail  logistics  and communications information media  entertainment and technology  industries by geography most of the revenue is derived from north america  and europe  corporate affairsedit marketing and brandingedit the companys flagship customer conference is cognizant community it is held annually in the united states europe australia and asia singapore india and japan the summit which features notable keynote speakers in the world of business technology economics and even adventure sports has been praised as a model industry event financeedit cognizant was listed on nasdaq in  and added to the nasdaq index in  after the close of trading on  november  cognizant moved from the mid cap sp  to the sp  the company claims it is in excellent financial health reporting over  billion in cash and short term investments for the quarter ending  september  net income for  was  billion as against  billion in  and  percent up in the fourth quarter to  million corporate social responsibilityedit cognizants philanthropic and corporate social responsibility csr initiatives are conducted through the cognizant employees for the financial and administrative support of the cognizant foundation registered in march  as a charitable company under the indian companies act the cognizant foundation aims to help unprivileged members of society gain access to quality education and healthcare by providing financial and technical support designing and implementing educational and healthcare improvement programs and partnering with nongovernment organizations ngos educational institutions healthcare institutions government agencies and corporations cognizant has a grassroots corporate social responsibility project called outreach for which cognizants employees volunteer to support schools and orphanages at the  maker faire the company announced plans to fund a maker space at the new york hall of science a making the future afterschool program and a partnership with citizen schools to promote stem education in the united states in  cognizant foundation made donation to vidnyanvahini a notforprofit organization located in pune in india for its mobile science laboratory msl environmental recordedit cognizants sustainability efforts include a go green initiative launched in  focused on energy conservation recycling and responsible waste management in october  newsweek magazine ranked cognizant th among the  largest publicly traded companies in america in its annual green rankings fortune edit year rank               othersedit on  june  the company signed a multimilliondollar agreement with escorts group in india to help escorts businesses in digital transformation and modernizing its operations across all business segments on  june  it partnered with singaporebased supermarket retailer ntuc fairprice to perform digital transformation in ntucs business to improve personalized and consistent customer service across multiple channels see alsoedit companies portal disney litigation francisco dsouza kumar mahadeva lakshmi narayanan srini raju tech companies in the new york city metropolitan region referencesedit  a b c d e  sec filing sec   cognizant technology solutions corporation ctsh seeking alpha retrieved may     a b c mishra pankaj  cognizant’s francisco d’souza the horizon chasers live mint and the wall street journal  march  retrieved on  from httpwwwlivemintcomcompaniesvduuoufvotxrmyarjjijcognizantsfranciscodsouzathehorizonchaserhtml  cognizant joins the fortune  club rediff  may  retrieved  june    worlds most admired companies information technology services  fortune retrieved  july    cognizant is like a billion tech startup retrieved    dun  bradstreet satyam to be rechristened cognizant tech business standard  february  retrieved  may    a b silvia sansoni  june  the contrarian forbes   no modest ambitions for cognizant express computer  october  retrieved  june    cognizant back in search of satyam business standard  april  retrieved  june    kumar mahadeva quits as cognizant chief   a b c d international directory of company histories vol st james press   dun  bradstreet spinoff will split in two the new york times  january  retrieved  june    rasheeda bhagat  february  cognizant rising by chennai beach the hindu retrieved  june    ims sees some positive impact from cognizant sale by eric auchard rediff  november    ist  cognizant founder steps down the hindu business line retrieved  june    anne vandermey  september  fastestgrowing  allstars forbes retrieved  june    cognizant in fortune  fortune retrieved  june    cognizant acquires trizetto bloomberg tv india  september    cognizant to